# Applications Directory

This directory contains application layer implementations that use the domain libraries.

## Structure

- `frontend/` - Frontend applications (Next.js, Remix, etc.)
- `backend/` - Backend services and APIs
- `mobile/` - Mobile applications (React Native, Expo)
- `desktop/` - Desktop applications (Electron, Tauri)

## Generated Applications

Applications are generated using the Copier templates:

```bash
# Generate Next.js application
copier copy templates/apps/nextjs-app ./apps/my-app

# Generate FastAPI backend
copier copy templates/apps/fastapi-api ./apps/api
```

Each application follows hexagonal architecture principles and integrates with domain libraries from `/libs/`.
